## Hard constraints

1. Deterministic only.
2. No LLM calls.
3. No browser automation.
4. No Selenium or Playwright.
5. No broker web scraping.
6. No hidden web-app APIs.
7. No unofficial Yahoo Finance scraping.
8. No `yfinance`.
9. No invented values.
10. Missing data must be explicitly reported.
11. Cache raw responses before normalization.
12. Every normalized value must include provenance.
13. API keys must never appear in outputs.
14. The tool must support offline rebuilds from cached raw files.

